title: Analyzing the Growth Dynamics of Bladder Cancer Using Ordinary Differential Equation Modeling
abstract: This analysis aims to explore the on-and off-target effects of a fibroblast growth factor receptor 3 (FGFR3) inhibitor aimed at slowing the growth of MB49 bladder cancer cells with a mutation in the FGFR3 gene that increases proliferation and decreases apoptosis.
